# Argo CD Application definitions for pipeline-app
#
# Prerequisites:
#   1. Argo CD installed on your K8s cluster
#   2. GitHub repo registered in Argo CD (Settings > Repositories)
#   3. Target namespaces created (pipeline-dev, pipeline-staging, pipeline-production)
#
# Apply with:
#   kubectl apply -f argocd/dev.yaml
#   kubectl apply -f argocd/staging.yaml
#   kubectl apply -f argocd/production.yaml
#
# Or apply the AppProject + all apps at once:
#   kubectl apply -f argocd/
